    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1879-05-13T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1879-05-13T00:00:00-05:00" n="457" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d457">
                <head>No. 426.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Hoffman</persName> to Mr. <persName type="to">Evarts</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of
                                    the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">St.
                                    Petersburg</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1879-05-13">
                            <hi rend="italic">May</hi> 13, 1879</date>.
                            (Received May 29.)</dateline>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 102.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: I have the honor to inform you that several
                        cases of cattle disease (<hi rend="italic">peste bovine</hi>) have appeared
                        at St. Petersburg, and that active measures have been taken to stamp it out.
                        Orders have been issued: <list>
                        <label>1st.</label>
                        <item>To kill all animals infected or supposed to be infected, paying
                                the owners therefor.</item>
                        <label>2d.</label>
                        <item>Forbidding the cattle at St. Petersburg to be allowed to graze in
                                common.</item>
                        <label>3d.</label>
                        <item>Establishing a strict veterinary inspection in all parts of the
                                city where the disease has already made, or may hereafter make, its
                                appearance.</item>
                    </list>
                </p>
                <p>Some thirty cases have been reported thus far.</p>
                <p>I have, &amp;c.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>WICKHAM HOFFMAN.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
